Package: RangeMap
Type: Package
Title: Range Map Workflow
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "An-Yu", 
           family = "Chang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "aychang4@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8860-5749"))
Description: This package provides a workflow for constructing species distribution
    models (SDM) using MaxEnt and generating range maps. The workflow involves   
    initializing a project structure, generating species data, constructing SDMs, 
    generating binary maps, creating range map layers for expert review, and producing 
    final range maps. The package aims to facilitate the efficient construction of SDMs 
    and the visualization of species range maps.
